  <span id="freeText8261009520571155499" style="display:none">Seizure (Virals #2) by Kathy Reichs<br /><br />I LOVE this series! It’s like Nancy Drew meets Maximum Ride. Seizure is the second book in the YA Virals series by Kathy Reichs author of the Temperance Brennan (Bones) novels. This series is inventive, intelligent and fun. <br /> <br />In Virals Tory and her friends are infected with a genetically altered parvo virus that affects their DNA and gives them special powers.<br /><br />In Seizure the gang is still trying to get the hang of what is happening to their bodies as well as searching for Anne Bonny’s pirate treasure.<br /><br />I truly cannot wait for the next installment.<br /></span>
