              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6729850894682458489">This book is freaking awesome. Fun, exciting, heart-stopping and surprising revelations and disappoints around every corner. Reichs makes a compelling story of enjoyable fiction with enough science and realistic situations that allow it to be a very palpable story. I thoroughly enjoyed every second and am already on to the next book!!!<br/>Also, felony count: six, I believe. These kids need a less illegal hobby lol</span>

          </span>
