<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/32073210-knit-yourself-calm"><img alt="Knit Yourself Calm: A Creative Path To Managing Stress" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1475992359l/32073210._SX98_.jpg" />
